Podcast interview via https://anchor.fm/intellectualexplorersclub/episodes/Peter-Boghossian---The-Great-Realignment-e3vobd

Peter Boghossian was involved in the 2nd 'Sokal Hoax' exposing  the weak editorial standards of academic outlets sympathetic to identity politics (the Grievance Studies affair). Doing this, the counter-pressure came from the left, while positive reactions streamed in from the right. This perplexed the left liberal Boghossian and sent him to a path of thinking about new political realignments.

Interviewer is Peter Limberg of the Intellectual Explorers Podcast.

